tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS historical_data (
    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(255),
    completion_year INT,
    project_type VARCHAR(50),
    architectural_style VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE architects (
  architect_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  architect_name TEXT,
  architect_specialization TEXT,
  architect_experience INT
)

CREATE TABLE historical_data (
  data_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name TEXT,
  completion_date DATE,
  location TEXT,
  architect_id UUID REFERENCES architects(architect_id)
)

CREATE TABLE architects (
	architect_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	architect_name VARCHAR(50),
	architect_specialization VARCHAR(50),
	architect_experience_years INT
)

CREATE TABLE historical_projects (

)

)
